name: Bitty Kitty #001
description: Adopt the very first Bitty Kitty! You can place this 3D kitten in the real world using Augmented Reality (AR). This first Bitty Kitty is based off of my own cat, Sandy, whom is extremely precious to me. Sandy turned 15 years old in May, 2021. Features that make Sandy unique, and are included in this Bitty Kitty, are: two big black dots around her nostrils, special coloured toes, a bent left ear tip, and cute fur patterns.
